headline: Textron Aviation to Open New Service Facility at Essendon Fields Airport, Expanding Capabilities in Australia
summary: WICHITA, Kan., February 17, 2025--Textron Aviation announced an Australia expansion with construction of a larger, modernized service facility at Essendon Fields Airport.
